TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source Qualifier to retreive the records from the source
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_STANDARD_COST

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT distinct TRIM(UPPER(APPLICATION_CD)) AS APPLICATION_CODE, TRIM(UPPER(PRODUCT_GRP_CD)) AS PRODUCT_GROUP_CODE, DECODE (TRIM(UPPER(APPLICATION_CD)), 'UCT','slu', 'ACI', 'tts', 'TTS', 'tts') AS DIVISION_GROUP, NVL(TRIM(STYLE_CD),' ' ) AS STYLE_NUM, NVL(TRIM(COLOR_CD),' ') AS COLOR_CODE, NVL(TRIM(SIZE_CD),' ' ) AS SIZE_CODE, NVL(TRIM(PCK_CD),' ') AS PACK_CODE, NVL(TRIM(XSZ_CD),' ' ) AS X_SIZE, NVL(TRIM(SZL_CD),' ' ) AS SIZE_LINE, NVL(TRIM(SZP_CD),' ' ) AS SIZE_POS, NVL(TRIM(ACTUAL_SIZE_NO),0) CUT_WIDTH, NVL(TRIM(ATTRIBUTE_CD),' ') AS ATTRIBUTION_CODE, STG_STANDARD_COST.COST_TYPE_CD, decode(TRIM(UPPER(PRODUCT_GRP_CD)),'SW',1,0 ) AS FLAG FROM STG_STANDARD_COST where TRIM(UPPER(APPLICATION_CD)) ||TRIM(UPPER(PRODUCT_GRP_CD)) IN ('UCTFS', 'TTSGS', 'ACIFS')
UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT APPLICATION_CODE as APPLICATION_CODE, PRODUCT_GROUP_CODE as PRODUCT_GROUP_CODE, DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP, STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM, COLOR_CODE as COLOR_CODE, SIZE_CODE as SIZE_CODE, PACK_CODE as PACK_CODE, X_SIZE as X_SIZE, SIZE_LINE as SIZE_LINE, SIZE_POS as SIZE_POS, CUT_WIDTH as CUT_WIDTH, ATTRIBUTION_CODE as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, COST_TYPE_CD as COST_TYPE_CD, FLAG as FLAG FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT APPLICATION_CODE as APPLICATION_CODE, PRODUCT_GROUP_CODE as PRODUCT_GROUP_CODE, DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP, STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM, COLOR_CODE as COLOR_CODE, SIZE_CODE as SIZE_CODE, PACK_CODE as PACK_CODE, X_SIZE as X_SIZE, SIZE_LINE as SIZE_LINE, SIZE_POS as SIZE_POS, CUT_WIDTH as CUT_WIDTH, ATTRIBUTION_CODE as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, COST_TYPE_CD as COST_TYPE_CD, FLAG as FLAG, RNK_SIZ AS RNK_SIZ FROM ( SELECT distinct TRIM(UPPER(APPLICATION_CD)) AS APPLICATION_CODE, decode(TRIM(UPPER(PRODUCT_GRP_CD)),'SW','CT',TRIM(UPPER(PRODUCT_GRP_CD)) ) AS PRODUCT_GROUP_CODE, DECODE (TRIM(UPPER(APPLICATION_CD)), 'UCT','slu', 'ACI', 'tts', 'TTS', 'tts') AS DIVISION_GROUP, NVL(TRIM(STYLE_CD),' ' ) AS STYLE_NUM, NVL(TRIM(COLOR_CD),' ') AS COLOR_CODE, NVL(TRIM(SIZE_CD),' ' )AS SIZE_CODE, NVL(TRIM(PCK_CD),' ') AS PACK_CODE, NVL(TRIM(XSZ_CD),' ' ) AS X_SIZE, NVL(TRIM(SZL_CD),' ' ) AS SIZE_LINE, NVL(TRIM(SZP_CD),' ' )AS SIZE_POS, NVL(TRIM(ACTUAL_SIZE_NO),0) CUT_WIDTH, NVL(TRIM(ATTRIBUTE_CD),' ') AS ATTRIBUTION_CODE, STG_STANDARD_COST.COST_TYPE_CD, decode(TRIM(UPPER(PRODUCT_GRP_CD)),'SW',1,0 ) AS FLAG, RANK () OVER ( partition BY APPLICATION_CD, TRIM(UPPER(PRODUCT_GRP_CD)), NVL(TRIM(STYLE_CD),' ' ), NVL(TRIM(SZL_CD),' ' ) , NVL(TRIM(SZP_CD),' ' ) ORDER BY NVL(TRIM(XSZ_CD),' ' ) asc ) AS rnk_siz FROM STG_STANDARD_COST where TRIM(UPPER(APPLICATION_CD)) ||TRIM(UPPER(PRODUCT_GRP_CD)) IN ('UCTCT','UCTSW') ) WHERE rnk_siz = 1 )
